race.description: Trotsynd - Join The Fun Ms Pace
race.comment: PRINCESS AVIATOR (5) has been racing well of late. Finished second at her latest appearance over 2130m at this track, beaten 2 metres. Meets a similar line up and she can take this out. OUR SERAPHINA (3) is in good form at present. Finished fourth at her latest appearance over 2130m here, beaten 3 metres. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw and is good enough to put herself in the winners' stall. THREE FLAMES (10) must be considered after she finished third over 2130m at this circuit a week ago. Top-three aspirations. ALTA GABBANA (13) is worth some thought despite her last-start sixth over 2130m at this course on December 6. Capable of bouncing back.
